flowchart LR
    ERR[API Error Response]

    ERR --> CODE[HTTP status code]
    ERR --> BODY[error body]
    BODY --> error_code[error_code\nmachine-readable]
    BODY --> message[message\nhuman-readable]
    BODY --> details[details\narray of field issues]
    BODY --> request_id

    CODE --> C4xx[4xx Client Errors]
    CODE --> C5xx[5xx Server Errors]

    C4xx --> RETRY{retriable?}
    C5xx --> RETRY

    RETRY -->|no: 400/403/404/409/410| DROP[do not retry]
    RETRY -->|yes: 429/500/502/503| BACKOFF[exponential backoff + jitter]
    RETRY -->|yes: 408/504| BACKOFF
    BACKOFF --> LIMIT{max attempts?}
    LIMIT -->|exceeded| DLQ[dead-letter / alert]
    LIMIT -->|ok| REQ[retry request]
